Dynamic-discovery backlinks block. Discovers the category's
`Show backlinks for` list via `#show` and renders one
`Category/backlink-row` per property. Skipped entirely when no
property has incoming links.

Auto-generated dispatchers bypass this path — they pre-build the
entire backlinks block with labels baked at generation time and
forward it via `backlink_section=` on `Category/table` /
`Category/sidebox`. Call this template directly only from
hand-written custom displays that want runtime discovery.

Parameter 1: category name (without namespace prefix).
</noinclude>
